ve team members for early intervention.</div><br> <div class="indentFlow">The EICM position allows for additional access above a service coordinator role.  Access may include creating and finalizing forms or editing of the student team. Both levels of access allow the ability to view the MDT.</div><br> <div class="indentFlow">School districts may elect to choose this option when the services coordinator will be the case manager for that birth through aged two child.  This is essentially the same role performed by a case manager for children aged three to twenty-one.</div>'
